Example01
=========
  Geant4 ExampleN01 adapted to Virtual Monte Carlo.

  Demonstrates:
    Simple geometry (Gsvolu, Gspos)
    Simple primary generator 
      one geantino with a fixed position and direction
    Access to particle in stepping

  See also description of in 
    geant4/examples/novice/N01/README


Macros:
=======

  For running example with G3:
  
  run_g3.C        - macro for running example 
  g3Config.C      - configuration macro for G3 with native geometry (default)
  g3tgeoConfig.C  - configuration macro for G3 with TGeo geometry
  test_g3.C       - macro for testing VMC geometry getters

  For running example with G4:
  
  run_g4.C    - macro for running example 
  g4Config.C  - configuration macro
  test_g4.C   - macro for testing VMC geometry getters
  
To run example:
===============
  
  With G3:
  root[0] .x run_g3.C  
  
  With G3 + TGeo:
  root[0] .x run_g3.C("g3tgeoConfig.C");  
  
  With G4:
  root[0] .x run_g4.C  
  
